---
import Page from '../layouts/Page.astro';
---

<Page
  title="All Star Party World — Miami's Ultimate Kids Party Venue"
  description="Miami's ultimate indoor kids party venue. 6,000 sq ft of exclusive fun — bounce houses, 2,500 sq ft blacklight glow room, laser tag, Nerf wars, arcade games & more. One party at a time."
>

  <!-- ── HERO ── -->
  <section class="hero" aria-label="All Star Party World">
    <div class="hero-bg" aria-hidden="true">
      <img src="/allstar-event-photos/glow-party-kids-dancing-blacklight-allstar-mural.jpg" alt="" />
    </div>
    <div class="hero-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="hero-top-bar" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="hero-content">
      <span class="eyebrow">01 · Kids Ages 4–12 · 8770 SW 131st St, Miami</span>
      <h1 class="hero-headline">
        ALL STAR<br>PARTY<br><span class="accent">WORLD.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        <strong>Miami's Ultimate Indoor Party Venue.</strong> 6,000 sq ft of fully air-conditioned fun — bounce houses, a 2,500 sq ft blacklight glow room, arcade games, and a team that handles everything so you don't have to.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/book" class="btn-primary"><i class="fa-regular fa-calendar" aria-hidden="true"></i> Book Your Event</a>
        <a href="#package" class="btn-outline">See What's Included</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stats" aria-label="Venue stats">
        <div>
          <div class="hero-stat-num">6K</div>
          <div class="hero-stat-label">Square Feet</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="hero-stat-num">ONE</div>
          <div class="hero-stat-label">Party at a Time</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="hero-stat-num">2HR</div>
          <div class="hero-stat-label">Private Party</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── ABOUT ── -->
  <section class="about-section" aria-label="About the Venue">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-img">
          <img src="/allstar-event-photos/party-room-view-basketball-court-with-balloons-and-tables.jpg" alt="All Star Party World — party room with basketball court, balloons, and tables set for celebration" />
        </div>
        <div class="about-copy">
          <p class="section-eyebrow">About The Venue</p>
          <h2 class="section-title">One Party.<br><span class="accent">Total Exclusivity.</span></h2>
          <p class="section-body">We only host one party at a time — so you and your guests have exclusive access to the entire 6,000 sq ft facility. No strangers, no overlapping events, just your people in your space.</p>
          <p class="section-body" style="margin-top:1rem;">Conveniently located next to the Falls Shopping Center — minutes from Pinecrest, Coral Gables, South Miami, and Kendall. Plenty of parking, fully air-conditioned, and ready for whatever adventure you have in mind.</p>
          <div class="about-actions">
            <a href="/book" class="btn-primary"><i class="fa-regular fa-calendar" aria-hidden="true"></i> Book Your Event</a>
            <a href="tel:+17864710100" class="btn-outline"><i class="fa-solid fa-phone" aria-hidden="true"></i> (786) 471-0100</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <!-- ── PHOTO STRIP ── -->
  <div class="photo-strip" aria-label="Venue photos">
    <div class="photo-strip-inner">
      <div class="photo-strip-item">
        <img src="/allstar-event-photos/inflatable-bounce-house-and-obstacle-course.jpg" alt="Inflatable bounce house and obstacle course" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="photo-strip-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="photo-strip-label">Bounce Houses</div>
      </div>
      <div class="photo-strip-item">
        <img src="/allstar-event-photos/laser-light-dance-floor-party.jpg" alt="Laser light dance floor party" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="photo-strip-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="photo-strip-label">Laser Tag</div>
      </div>
      <div class="photo-strip-item">
        <img src="/allstar-event-photos/kids-playing-classic-arcade-games-pacman-mario.jpg" alt="Kids playing classic arcade games" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="photo-strip-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="photo-strip-label">Arcade Games</div>
      </div>
      <div class="photo-strip-item">
        <img src="/allstar-event-photos/kids-playing-basketball-arcade-shootout-machines.jpg" alt="Kids playing basketball arcade shootout machines" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="photo-strip-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="photo-strip-label">Sports Area</div>
      </div>
      <div class="photo-strip-item">
        <img src="/allstar-event-photos/kids-parachute-game-activity-party.jpg" alt="Kids enjoying parachute game party activity" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="photo-strip-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="photo-strip-label">Group Activities</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <!-- ── THE SPACE ── -->
  <section class="space-section" aria-label="The Facility">
    <div class="section-inner" style="padding-top:3.5rem;">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">The Facility</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Everything You Need<br><span class="accent">All In One Place.</span></h2>
      <p class="section-body">From the bounce area to the blacklight room — every corner is built to keep kids moving, laughing, and having the time of their lives.</p>

      <div class="included-grid">
        <div class="included-cell">
          <div class="included-num">6K SQ FT</div>
          <div class="included-title">Private Venue</div>
          <div class="included-desc">Fully air-conditioned and exclusively yours. No public access, no shared time slots.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="included-cell">
          <div class="included-num">2,500</div>
          <div class="included-title">Blacklight Glow Room</div>
          <div class="included-desc">Custom spray-painted blacklight room — dodge ball, freeze tag, basketball, and scooter soccer under the glow.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="included-cell">
          <div class="included-num">BOUNCE</div>
          <div class="included-title">Bounce Area</div>
          <div class="included-desc">Full-size bounce houses that keep kids entertained from the moment they walk in.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="included-cell">
          <div class="included-num">SPORTS</div>
          <div class="included-title">Sports Area</div>
          <div class="included-desc">Basketball, ping-pong, and a full-size Connect Four game — friendly competition for every age.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="included-cell">
          <div class="included-num">ARCADE</div>
          <div class="included-title">Old-School Video Games</div>
          <div class="included-desc">Full-sized vintage arcade games. Adults play too — nobody sits this one out.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="included-cell">
          <div class="included-num">VIP</div>
          <div class="included-title">Adult Viewing Room</div>
          <div class="included-desc">A glassed viewing room with 2 TVs, ESPN, Dominos, and Ping-Pong for the adults who want to keep an eye on the fun.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <!-- ── ULTIMATE PACKAGE ── -->
  <section id="package" class="pkg-section" aria-label="The Signature Package">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">The Signature Package</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Ultimate All-Star<br><span class="accent">Party Package.</span></h2>
      <p class="section-body">A two-hour private party with exclusive access to the full facility. Designed for every age group — boys and girls alike.</p>

      <div class="pkg-highlight">
        <div class="pkg-highlight-grid">
          <div>
            <p class="pkg-label">What's Included</p>
            <ul class="pkg-list">
              <li>2-hour exclusive venue rental</li>
              <li>30 minutes early access to set up the party room</li>
              <li>Bounce house, ping-pong &amp; full-size Connect Four</li>
              <li>2,500 sq ft blacklight glow room with dodge ball, freeze tag, basketball &amp; scooter soccer</li>
              <li>Pizza &amp; drinks for up to 25 children</li>
              <li>Cake table, food tables &amp; gift table</li>
              <li>6 tables with bench seating</li>
              <li>4 party specialists — setup, check-in, music &amp; activities</li>
              <li>Adult viewing room with 2 TVs, Dominos &amp; arcade games</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="pkg-note">
              <strong>Good to know:</strong> Each additional child is $25. Outside food &amp; beverages are welcome. Extra time can be purchased based on availability. Socks and signed waivers are required for all participating guests.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="pkg-img-wrap">
              <img src="/allstar-event-photos/toddler-interactive-touchscreen-bear-game.jpg" alt="Kids enjoying interactive games at All Star Party World" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
            <div class="pkg-actions">
              <a href="/book" class="btn-primary" style="flex:1;justify-content:center;"><i class="fa-regular fa-calendar" aria-hidden="true"></i> Book Now</a>
              <a href="/balloon-packages" class="btn-outline" style="flex:1;justify-content:center;"><i class="fa-solid fa-wand-sparkles" aria-hidden="true"></i> Add Decorations</a>
            </div>
            <p class="pkg-fine-print">20% Facility Fee + 7% Sales Tax added to all packages. Call for current pricing.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── STATS STRIP ── -->
  <div class="stats-strip" aria-label="Quick stats">
    <div class="stats-inner">
      <div>
        <div class="stat-num">6K</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Square Feet</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="stat-num">1</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Party at a Time</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="stat-num">4</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Party Specialists</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="stat-num">5★</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Average Rating</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── EVENTS WE HOST ── -->
  <section id="events" class="events-section" aria-label="Events We Host">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">What We Host</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Your Event.<br><span class="accent">Our Expertise.</span></h2>
      <div class="events-grid">

        <div class="event-card">
          <div class="event-card-img">
            <img src="/allstar-event-photos/party-room-view-basketball-court-with-balloons-and-tables.jpg" alt="Kids birthday party setup" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="event-card-body">
            <div class="event-tag">Most Popular</div>
            <h3 class="event-title">Birthday Parties</h3>
            <p class="event-desc">The ultimate birthday for kids ages 4–12. Custom theme, full glow room, bounce house, and a party team that makes every child feel like the star.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="event-card">
          <div class="event-card-img">
            <img src="/allstar-event-photos/glow-party-kids-dancing-blacklight-allstar-mural.jpg" alt="Glow party in blacklight room" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="event-card-body">
            <div class="event-tag">Themed Experience</div>
            <h3 class="event-title">Glow Party</h3>
            <p class="event-desc">2,500 sq ft of custom blacklight murals and glow-in-the-dark everything. The most unique party environment in Miami — period.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="event-card">
          <div class="event-card-img">
            <img src="/allstar-event-photos/laser-light-dance-floor-party.jpg" alt="Laser tag and Nerf wars" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="event-card-body">
            <div class="event-tag">Action Packed</div>
            <h3 class="event-title">Nerf Wars &amp; Laser Tag</h3>
            <p class="event-desc">Add Nerf Wars or Laser Tag to any package and watch the energy level triple. Fully managed by our team.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="event-card">
          <div class="event-card-img">
            <img src="/allstar-event-photos/kids-parachute-game-activity-party.jpg" alt="Kids class party group activity" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="event-card-body">
            <div class="event-tag">School Event</div>
            <h3 class="event-title">End-of-Year &amp; Class Parties</h3>
            <p class="event-desc">Send the school year off right. We host full class parties with activities that keep every kid busy — teachers included.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="event-card">
          <div class="event-card-img">
            <img src="/allstar-event-photos/kids-playing-classic-arcade-games-pacman-mario.jpg" alt="Family reunion arcade fun" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="event-card-body">
            <div class="event-tag">Family</div>
            <h3 class="event-title">Family Reunions</h3>
            <p class="event-desc">Keep the kids busy in the bounce and glow areas while the adults catch up in the viewing room. Everyone's entertained, nobody's stressed.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="event-card">
          <div class="event-card-img">
            <img src="/allstar-event-photos/adult-playing-street-basketball-arcade-machine.jpg" alt="Corporate family day at All Star" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="event-card-body">
            <div class="event-tag">Corporate</div>
            <h3 class="event-title">Company Family Days</h3>
            <p class="event-desc">Reward your team with a day the whole family loves. Your company becomes legendary — and the kids won't stop talking about it Monday morning.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <!-- ── PARTY EXTRAS ── -->
  <section id="extras" class="extras-section" aria-label="Party Add-Ons and Upgrades">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">Add-Ons &amp; Upgrades</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Make It a<br><span class="accent">Super Party.</span></h2>
      <p class="section-body">Add any of these to your package and turn a great party into an unforgettable one. Don't see what you want? Just ask.</p>

      <div class="extras-grid">
        <div class="extra-item">
          <div class="extra-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-music" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
          <div>
            <div class="extra-name">Live DJ</div>
            <div class="extra-desc">Pro DJ keeping the energy high all party long.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="extra-item">
          <div class="extra-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-star" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
          <div>
            <div class="extra-name">Glow Party Lighting</div>
            <div class="extra-desc">Full blacklight and neon lighting upgrade for the ultimate glow experience.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="extra-item">
          <div class="extra-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-microphone" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
          <div>
            <div class="extra-name">Karaoke</div>
            <div class="extra-desc">Singing sound booth — everyone gets their moment on the mic.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="extra-item">
          <div class="extra-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-crosshairs" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
          <div>
            <div class="extra-name">Nerf Wars</div>
            <div class="extra-desc">Nerf darts and safety goggles included. Fully managed battle zone.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="extra-item">
          <div class="extra-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-gun" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
          <div>
            <div class="extra-name">Laser Tag</div>
            <div class="extra-desc">Latest laser technology. No mess, no noise, all the intensity.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="extra-item">
          <div class="extra-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-football" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
          <div>
            <div class="extra-name">Football Experience</div>
            <div class="extra-desc">NFL-inspired football experience. Did someone say NFL?</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="extra-item">
          <div class="extra-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-paint-brush" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
          <div>
            <div class="extra-name">Paint Me One Session</div>
            <div class="extra-desc">Splatter painting session — messy, creative, and totally memorable.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="extra-item">
          <div class="extra-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
          <div>
            <div class="extra-name">Extreme Gaga Ball</div>
            <div class="extra-desc">A high-energy pit game every kid gets obsessed with instantly.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="extra-item">
          <div class="extra-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-hand" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
          <div>
            <div class="extra-name">Claw Machine</div>
            <div class="extra-desc">Unlimited tries — so everyone wins. Zero frustration guaranteed.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="extra-item">
          <div class="extra-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-camera" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
          <div>
            <div class="extra-name">Photo Booth — Traditional</div>
            <div class="extra-desc">Dual camera with unlimited prints. Instant takeaway for every guest.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="extra-item">
          <div class="extra-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-rotate" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
          <div>
            <div class="extra-name">Photo Booth — 360°</div>
            <div class="extra-desc">360-degree video booth with a dedicated attendant. The moment everyone shares.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="extra-item">
          <div class="extra-icon" style="font-size:1.1rem;">🍿</div>
          <div>
            <div class="extra-name">Popcorn</div>
            <div class="extra-desc">Freshly popped during your party for all guests to enjoy.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="extra-item">
          <div class="extra-icon" style="font-size:1.1rem;">🍬</div>
          <div>
            <div class="extra-name">Cotton Candy</div>
            <div class="extra-desc">Hand-spun during the party. Guests choose their own flavor.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="extra-item">
          <div class="extra-icon" style="font-size:1.1rem;">🧊</div>
          <div>
            <div class="extra-name">Snow Cones</div>
            <div class="extra-desc">Shaved ice with many flavors to choose from. A Miami must.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="extra-item">
          <div class="extra-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-wand-sparkles" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
          <div>
            <div class="extra-name">Balloon Decorations</div>
            <div class="extra-desc">4 packages available. Arches, columns, centerpieces — any theme.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="extra-item extra-item--custom">
          <div class="extra-icon extra-icon--custom"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
          <div>
            <div class="extra-name">Don't See It?</div>
            <div class="extra-desc">Just ask — we can put together any adventure, large or small.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <!-- ── CTA ── -->
  <section class="cta-section" aria-label="Book your event">
    <div class="section-inner" style="text-align:center;padding-top:4rem;padding-bottom:4rem;">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">Ready to Celebrate?</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Let's Make It<br><span class="accent">Unforgettable.</span></h2>
      <p class="cta-body">Fill out our booking form and our team will reach out within 24 hours with availability, pricing, and a custom proposal for your child's big day.</p>
      <div class="cta-actions">
        <a href="/book" class="btn-primary"><i class="fa-regular fa-calendar" aria-hidden="true"></i> Book Your Event</a>
        <a href="tel:+17864710100" class="btn-outline"><i class="fa-solid fa-phone" aria-hidden="true"></i> (786) 471-0100</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── FAQ ── -->
  <section class="faq-section" aria-label="Frequently Asked Questions">
    <div class="section-inner faq-header-inner">
      <div style="text-align:center;">
        <p class="section-eyebrow">Questions</p>
        <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-bottom:0;">Frequently Asked</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list-wrap">
      <div class="faq-list" role="list">

        <div class="faq-item" role="listitem">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-as-1">
            <span>Who is All Star Party World for?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-as-1" role="region">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">All Star Party World is designed for kids ages 4–12. Our Ultimate Package was built for every age group — boys and girls alike. From birthday parties and glow parties to school events and corporate family days, if kids are involved, we've got it covered.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" role="listitem">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-as-2">
            <span>Is the whole venue just for my party?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-as-2" role="region">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">Yes — we only host one party at a time. When you book All Star Party World, you get exclusive access to the entire 6,000 sq ft facility. No strangers, no overlap, no sharing.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" role="listitem">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-as-3">
            <span>What's included in the Ultimate Package?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-as-3" role="region">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">The Ultimate Package includes 2 hours of exclusive venue access (plus 30 minutes early setup), bounce house, 2,500 sq ft blacklight glow room with dodge ball/freeze tag/basketball/scooter soccer, ping-pong, Connect Four, pizza and drinks for up to 25 kids, 4 party specialists, cake table, food and gift tables, and 6 tables with bench seating.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" role="listitem">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-as-4">
            <span>Can I bring my own food?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-as-4" role="region">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">Yes — outside food and beverages are welcome. We also offer a full catering menu if you'd rather let us handle it. Pizza and drinks for up to 25 kids are included in the base package.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" role="listitem">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-as-5">
            <span>What are Party Extras and how do I add them?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-as-5" role="region">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">Party Extras are add-ons that upgrade your event — Laser Tag, Nerf Wars, Karaoke, 360 Photo Booth, Cotton Candy, Snow Cones, and more. Just mention which ones you want when booking and we'll build them into your custom proposal.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item" role="listitem">
          <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-as-6">
            <span>Do you have a teen and adult venue nearby?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-as-6" role="region">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">Yes — The 305 Club is our sister venue for teens and adults, located at the same address. Perfect for multi-generational events: the kids celebrate at All Star Party World while the older crowd enjoys Miami's premier nightclub-style event space. One call, two venues.</div>
